# Environment Variables for Feedback System
# Copy this to .env.local and fill in your values

# GitHub Personal Access Token (for creating issues)
# Create fine-grained token at: https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new
# Repository: gpt-pinboard-extension (selected repositories only)
# Permissions needed: Issues (Read and write), Metadata (Read)
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_token_here

# That's it! Your feedback system only needs the GitHub token.
# 
# The system automatically:
# - Creates GitHub issues for feedback
# - Provides fallback email links if API fails
# - No additional email service needed